  "base_path": "/pay-court-fine-online",
  "content_id": "6ae16c12-a554-44e2-b3e3-596375aa1b9a",
  "description": "The only service you can use to pay your court fine online, or by telephone using a credit or debit card.",
  "details": {
    "body": "<p>You can pay a court fine or charge online or by phone.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>This page is also available <a href=\"/talu-dirwy-llys-ar-lein\">in Welsh (Cymraeg)</a>.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>You can use this service to pay the following in England and Wales:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>court fines</li>\n  <li>compensation</li>\n  <li>victims surcharge</li>\n  <li>prosecutor costs</li>\n  <li>criminal courts charge</li>\n  <li>confiscation orders</li>\n  <li>fixed penalties that have been registered in a magistrates’ court</li>\n  <li>vehicle excise back duty</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>There are different services for paying <a href=\"/court-fees-what-they-are\">court fees</a> and <a href=\"/parking-tickets/paying-a-ticket\">parking tickets</a>.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>There’s a different way to <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.nidirect.gov.uk/articles/court-fines\">pay in Northern Ireland</a> and <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.scotcourts.gov.uk/taking-action/pay-a-fine\">pay in Scotland</a>.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"how-to-pay\">How to pay</h2>\n\n<p>You need your ‘notice of fine’ and a debit or credit card. If you’ve lost your notice of fine, <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.find-court-tribunal.service.gov.uk/\">contact the court</a> where you received the fine.</p>\n\n<p>You must pay by the date given in your notice of fine. The court might reject your payment if enforcement action has already started.</p>\n\n<p>If you were fined at a <a href=\"/courts/crown-court\">Crown Court</a>, you need your account number and division code.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"pay-online\">Pay online</h3>\n\n<p>You can pay online using the court fines service.</p>\n\n<p><a class=\"gem-c-button govuk-button govuk-button--start\" role=\"button\" data-module=\"govuk-button\" draggable=\"false\" href=\"https://courtfines.justice.gov.uk/courtfines/pages/preselect.do\"><span> Start now </span><svg class=\"govuk-button__start-icon govuk-!-display-none-print\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"17.5\" height=\"19\" viewbox=\"0 0 33 40\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M0 0h13l20 20-20 20H0l20-20z\"></path></svg></a></p>\n\n<h3 id=\"pay-by-phone\">Pay by phone</h3>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p>Telephone: 0300 790 9901 (in England)<br>\nTelephone: 0300 790 9980 (in Wales)<br>\n<a href=\"/call-charges\">Find out about call charges</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h3 id=\"other-ways-to-pay\">Other ways to pay</h3>\n\n<p>Contact the Enforcement Office listed on the notice of fine to pay by direct debit, payment card or bank transfer.</p>\n",
    "external_related_links": [

    ]
  },
